            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Resourcefulness enables characters to turn limited tools or surroundings into solutions on the fly. Whether it\u2019s crafting a rope from vines to cross a chasm, using a shattered shield as a sled down an icy slope, or repurposing a glowing crystal to signal for help, this expertise thrives on ingenuity. It\u2019s the mark of an adventurer who can seize opportunity from chaos, making it invaluable in a world where preparation often meets the unexpected.",
                "marks": [],
